{"tid":1846912,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(已fc)HKU要求一村hall準備隔離層俾大陸學生自我隔離","createTime":"2020-01-27T19:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T03:33:03.000Z","uid":168758,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b4dfa93a380e1741f039d118cff91f8735f4f447","tid":1846912,"uid":168758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aH27NLB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaH27NLB.png&h=f45164cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1BhzsLB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1BhzsLB.png&h=bf98267d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你hku係唔係on9㗎 叫住低層個啲一日內清好房 一係搬上樓上(屌都未必有位) 一係就搬走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最on9嘅係要同班隔離緊既大陸人住埋同一棟樓 屌咁點隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />萬一當中真係有人瀨咗嘢 咁係唔係成間hall嘅人全部要隔離呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大陸人係hall係佔少數㗎咋 點解要local同埋外國人就矖佢地 叫啲大陸學生咪撚落黎係唔係仲有效呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌 都唔知有無問過附近民居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 住過 已grad <br />\n<br />\n📣🔈❗Urgent Message❗*Subject to the official announcement from hall office later tongiht*<br />\nIn light of the past SARS experience (7-week class suspension) and the press release from Professor Gabriel Leung (Dean of Faculty of Medicine)stating that the situation may escalate in the coming months, our hall will implement several policies including setting up *Quarantine Floors* in order to safeguard our hallmate's health, life and wellbeing. Since students from the affected areas are returning to hall in coming days, we have to clear several lower floors (accessible through stairs) for the time being to act as Quarantine Floors *by tomorrow (28 Jan 2020)* <br />\n<br />\nThere are several ways to clear your rooms <br />\n<br />\n(1) Come back to tidy up by yourself<br />\n(2) Ask your friends to tidy up<br />\n(3) Office to tidy up and store your stuff safely <br />\n<br />\nYou may choose to <br />\n(1) Check out from hall (encouraged)<br />\n(2) Store your things at hall <br />\n(3) Move to a room on upper floors<br />\n<br />\nIn return for your kind cooperation, we will <br />\n(1) *Refund the hall fees paid* (amount to be discussed) if you quit the hall tomorrow. <br />\n(2) *You can check in again as soon as school starts again*."},{"pid":"868090ca0dc2edb0825b9a5125b90d068e97f883","tid":1846912,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:21:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eda67a36a5f07120df0d843edd82fb63b3f7e27a","tid":1846912,"uid":168758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:21:32.000Z","msg":"十連 1/10"},{"pid":"c6ff87bb143393f6cb11df47b1f89eddc2bc2b52","tid":1846912,"uid":168758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:21:45.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"f0f6cc0f5c457e38ade56a4a6f660e2b68491ef0","tid":1846912,"uid":168758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:21:56.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"2aab38d4cf92b0199a3db3cb6b57eb967f6d06f2","tid":1846912,"uid":135124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:22:14.000Z","msg":"On9架 一村隔離就係寶翠園<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722aca29e64311f73f41cf1cd3922e0d85e461a8","tid":1846912,"uid":168758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:22:24.000Z","msg":"HKU奶共到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 4/10"},{"pid":"42291470c8dbe06721fb0294f3e35c3e9b2ce454","tid":1846912,"uid":168758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:22:36.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"78728b657bd60cd2f8a9aabafe039ff50f8be6de","tid":1846912,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:22:36.000Z","msg":"正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷工有咩做？不如包圍政府相關設施！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846866\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846866</a>"},{"pid":"ed50ad4f8cae48d9cef3840b72afd1e5d84d4f75","tid":1846912,"uid":168758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:22:56.000Z","msg":"推到hku撤回!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"03139aa3f74c03e91920984f776024b6c4085680","tid":1846912,"uid":168758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:23:15.000Z","msg":"6/1